{"tid":2113414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"40年前《中英聯合聲明》出現時香港人已指出過是盲婚啞嫁。","createTime":"2020-07-18T06:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T06:09:07.000Z","uid":261647,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a4bbc3e67a953dfd0c750a6e556bb483073e0e65","tid":2113414,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:02:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20200717064330/https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1269938153021796352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20200717064330%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1269938153021796352&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTifGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=8f2710dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20200717064330/https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1269938153021796352</a><br />\n<br />\n說當年香港人接受一國兩制，完全錯誤。當年香港公眾只聽過「中國收返香港」，從沒有知道所謂「香港回歸中國」，後來他們很多人受到傳媒洗腦後奇怪地從眾轉軚是另一回事。40年前《中英聯合聲明》出現時香港人已指出過是盲婚啞嫁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B064fyb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB064fyb.jpg&h=838067ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20200717064731/https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1269937677333217282\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20200717064731%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1269937677333217282&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTifGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=23b71a07\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20200717064731/https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1269937677333217282</a><br />\n<br />\n我們香港人有香港主權嗎？沒有就只是殖民地。香港需要的是殖民地獨立，不是做中國殖民地。中國現在是殖民香港，香港的去殖民化是要去中國化。"},{"pid":"45a8c471de2b028ccd4fb2adadde539c80d4b524","tid":2113414,"uid":301989,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:09:07.000Z","msg":"多謝李柱銘屍屠華爭取支那獨裁統治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}